Third-party data:

This project evaluates models on ADE Corpus v2 (Gurulingappa et al., 2012),
loaded via the HuggingFace Datasets hub (`ade_corpus_v2`). The dataset is
not redistributed by this repository; licensing terms for the corpus are
determined by the dataset provider and should be consulted at
https://huggingface.co/datasets/ade_corpus_v2 before redistribution or
commercial use.
